OL,3,CPolice and Liverpool FC join forces to
OL,4,Ctackle violence against women and girls
OL,6,FAround 80 girls from across Merseyside
OL,7,Fhave taken part in an event focused on
OL,8,Feducating young people about Violence
OL,9,FAgainst Women and Girls (VAWG).
OL,11,FA month-long campaign has seen
OL,12,Fofficers carry out VAWG presentations
OL,13,Fin front of secondary school pupils
OL,14,Facross Merseyside, with the help of
OL,15,Fthe LFC Foundation, a charity set up
OL,16,Fby Liverpool Football Club to tackle
OL,17,Fsocial inequality.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
