CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773346285
OL,3,CPolice and Liverpool FC join forces to
OL,4,Ctackle violence against women and girls
OL,6,FThe presentation highlights the work
OL,7,Fbeing done by Merseyside Police to
OL,8,Fkeep women and girls safe and tackle
OL,9,Fthe causes of VAWG.
OL,11,FFaye Smith, Safer Schools Coordinator
OL,12,Fat Merseyside Police, said: "Today's
OL,13,Fevent is part of a month-long focus in
OL,14,Fschools across Merseyside, where we
OL,15,Ftalk openly with young people about
OL,16,FViolence Against Women and Girls.
OL,26,@tD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
