FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773346285
OL,3,CPolice and Liverpool FC join forces to
OL,4,Ctackle violence against women and girls
OL,6,F"The work we do with young people is
OL,7,Fvital and these conversations help
OL,8,Fthem understand what is and isn't
OL,9,Facceptable, particularly around
OL,10,Fabusive or misogynistic behaviours."
OL,12,FThroughout the day, attendees took
OL,13,Fpart in workshops exploring healthy
OL,14,Frelationships, consent, self-esteem,
OL,15,Fonline safety, exploitation, gender
OL,16,Fstereotypes, and confidence.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
