PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773346285
OL,3,CPolice and Liverpool FC join forces to
OL,4,Ctackle violence against women and girls
OL,6,FFaye said: "We have a real opportunity
OL,7,Fto make a difference, and we're
OL,8,Fcommitted to spreading that message.
OL,9,FEvents like this are about
OL,10,Fempowerment, giving girls the
OL,11,Fknowledge, confidence and voice to
OL,12,Frecognise their worth, challenge
OL,13,Fharmful behaviours and support one
OL,14,Fanother."
OL,26,@nD@LOUvD@IO]
