PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773346285
OL,3,CPolice and Liverpool FC join forces to
OL,4,Ctackle violence against women and girls
OL,6,FMatt Parish, CEO of LFC Foundation,
OL,7,Fadded: "It's vital we work in
OL,8,Fpartnership with Merseyside Police to
OL,9,Fhelp educate young people about the
OL,10,Fissues surrounding violence against
OL,11,FWomen and Girls, using the power of
OL,12,Fthe Liverpool Football Club badge.
OL,14,F"Working in partnership is where real
OL,15,Fchange can happen, and our Youth
OL,16,FInterventions team do a fantastic job
OL,17,Fday to day in helping young people
OL,18,Ftalk openly about this topic.
OL,26,@oD@HOUvD@AOU
